Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.87,0:00:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我是MDMM株式公司的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.27,0:00:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,第二代社长的秘书
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.35,0:00:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,秘书不只是听从命令
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.42,0:00:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,要管理上司的日程资料\N喜欢的咖啡高级宾馆
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.83,0:00:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,破除上司不知道的不良传言
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.37,0:00:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,（主演白木优子）\N要完美的解决上司的烦恼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.11,0:00:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,作为秘书理解是很重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.99,0:01:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.12,0:01:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我是MDMM公司的\N秘书白木
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.13,0:01:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,社长想今天和你开会
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.20,0:01:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,可以让高保社长接电话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.48,0:01:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.75,0:01:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,要是回来了可以回电话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.89,0:01:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.09,0:01:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,那么拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.30,0:01:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,社长 掘岛贵文
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.50,0:01:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,那个穷社长说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.44,0:01:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,现在出去了四点半回来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.18,0:01:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,这是要我们给他打电话
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.45,0:02:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.85,0:02:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,太忙了不能接电话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.59,0:02:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,肯定没想工作的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.46,0:02:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,但高保社长是之前就合作的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.34,0:02:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你只是个秘书态度很傲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.08,0:02:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,可以不做这个
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.15,0:02:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我也想雇佣年轻漂亮的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.75,0:02:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我是少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.69,0:02:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.30,0:02:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,上任社长要我做到最后
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.30,0:02:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,不是简单就可以开除的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.64,0:03:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,真的好麻烦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.25,0:03:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,那个死老头
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.05,0:03:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,不能说你爸爸的坏话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.59,0:03:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,好的知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.53,0:03:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,对了我要去开派对了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.93,0:03:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,准备车
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.07,0:03:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,社长今天傍晚有会
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.21,0:03:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,是公司内部会议之后会餐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.14,0:03:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊公司内部会议你可以的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.55,0:03:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,还是调整一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.76,0:03:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.49,0:03:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,那么我就走了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.83,0:04:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,对了给我按摩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.70,0:04:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.60,0:04:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,社长
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.67,0:04:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你儿子很不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.74,0:04:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,真的爱孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.15,0:04:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,但是差不多少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.62,0:04:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,要教导一下了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.69,0:05:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,（五年前）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.83,0:05:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,白木
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.37,0:05:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我儿子会继承我的公司
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.71,0:05:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,可以像对我一样在他身边
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.25,0:05:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,支持他吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.45,0:05:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,（元社长 掘岛贵一）\N我这样说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.92,0:05:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,他没经营的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.33,0:05:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,很会花钱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.60,0:05:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,最近一直买高级车和手表
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.40,0:05:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,真的很愁人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.48,0:05:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我只有这一个儿子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.28,0:06:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,可能太溺爱孩子了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.89,0:06:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,但很可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.90,0:06:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.10,0:06:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我理解您的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.31,0:06:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,就交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.11,0:06:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,肯定会成为好的社长的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.66,0:06:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,（精英淫语 淫荡秘书）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.81,0:06:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,这里好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.34,0:06:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,就是这里有点疼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.28,0:07:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,这样好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.95,0:07:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,那个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.49,0:07:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,那个穷社长怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.96,0:07:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,高保社长吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.30,0:07:17.89,Default,,0,0,0,,很顺利
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.83,0:07:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢了不亏是优子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.04,0:07:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,帮大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.17,0:07:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,不要喊优子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.18,0:07:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,好的知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.05,0:07:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,白木
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.92,0:07:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,社长我现在说一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.06,0:07:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,社员对你评价不好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.40,0:07:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.60,0:07:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,他们拿了这么多钱还抱恕
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.74,0:08:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么想
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.81,0:08:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,是社长不称职
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.55,0:08:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,要好好做社长
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.76,0:08:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,知道了我也在想
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.96,0:08:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,真的好累啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.97,0:08:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,好困
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.23,0:08:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,睡着了继续做
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.24,0:08:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.77,0:08:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,白木
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.52,0:08:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.19,0:08:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,香槟呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.63,0:09:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,社长打开了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.13,0:10:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,肩膀很僵硬吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.96,0:10:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.23,0:10:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,社长有感觉了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.84,0:10:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你在做什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.24,0:10:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,在按摩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.38,0:10:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.05,0:10:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么这样叫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.25,0:10:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,没什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.99,0:11:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我累的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.33,0:11:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,这里累了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.06,0:11:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,这里没有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.94,0:11:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.94,0:11:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.34,0:11:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你哪里累了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.68,0:11:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,这里没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.95,0:11:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.89,0:11:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,是社长的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.83,0:11:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,好好睡觉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.83,0:11:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下要好好听我的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.10,0:11:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,是秘书才替社长的身体考虑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.84,0:12:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,不要继续了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.78,0:12:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,不是精油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.12,0:12:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.12,0:12:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.53,0:12:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,但是乳头硬了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.33,0:12:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,不是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.54,0:12:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.94,0:12:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,那这里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.48,0:12:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.28,0:12:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下啊不要
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.88,0:12:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起想要这个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.42,0:12:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,在做什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.63,0:12:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,那么请吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.97,0:12:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.18,0:13:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.78,0:13:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,今天你很奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.12,0:13:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.72,0:13:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,但是社长舔我的乳头了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.99,0:13:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.86,0:13:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,大小不一样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.33,0:13:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,-不是的 -这里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.40,0:13:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,乳头也大了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.48,0:13:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,舔了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.22,0:13:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,可以了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.82,0:13:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起是两个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.49,0:13:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.50,0:13:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,请吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.17,0:14:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,乳头好硬啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.98,0:14:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,不是的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.18,0:14:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,是真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.72,0:14:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.06,0:14:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,-不要啊 -这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.87,0:14:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,肉棒硬了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.54,0:14:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,真的不行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.34,0:14:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,今天不要按摩了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.21,0:14:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,社长说的和身体
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.82,0:14:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,不一样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.56,0:14:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,这样社员不会相信的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.36,0:15:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.36,0:15:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,-怎么了 -今天就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.16,0:15:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.10,0:15:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.70,0:15:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.37,0:15:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,今天可以回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.64,0:15:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.71,0:15:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,做什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.91,0:15:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,想全部都做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.45,0:15:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.33,0:15:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,-这样 -不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.87,0:15:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会怎么样的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.74,0:15:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,那脱内裤看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.07,0:15:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.28,0:15:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.08,0:15:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,社长这不是硬了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.68,0:15:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,现在有点困
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.15,0:16:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.82,0:16:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,-可以睡觉的 -不要
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.90,0:16:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.90,0:16:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,在摸哪里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.44,0:16:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,不喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.44,0:16:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,就别勃起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.65,0:16:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.05,0:16:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,不要勃起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.18,0:16:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,这个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.19,0:16:34.45,Default,,0,0,0,,肉棒硬了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.32,0:16:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.06,0:16:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.53,0:16:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我是社长的秘书
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.73,0:16:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,知道社长想做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.60,0:16:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下不要这样子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.81,0:16:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.76,0:17:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,知道在做什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.44,0:17:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,社长刚才摸了我的乳头
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.11,0:17:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,社长这里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.98,0:17:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,已经这么硬了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.85,0:17:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.98,0:17:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,乳头都这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.45,0:17:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我什么都没做
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.86,0:17:45.59,Default,,0,0,0,,可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.06,0:17:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,不会告诉别人的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.60,0:17:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下要出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.21,0:18:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,很遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.96,0:18:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.09,0:18:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,已经不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.70,0:18:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,还没结束呢你看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.23,0:18:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,还在按摩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.04,0:18:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,在做什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.98,0:18:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,想要胸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.86,0:18:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.46,0:18:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,还有屁股
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.40,0:19:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,真的很可爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.48,0:19:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,很喜欢这样刺激吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.68,0:19:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,在做什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.62,0:19:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,社长这样子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.82,0:19:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,已经这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.70,0:19:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,不是我这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.50,0:19:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,社长的威严呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.17,0:19:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,是水吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.58,0:19:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,好像有水出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.92,0:19:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.66,0:19:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,继续舔吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.59,0:20:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,社长
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.73,0:20:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,可以了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.93,0:20:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,和很多女生做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.73,0:20:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.87,0:20:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,和平常一样舔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.41,0:20:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.68,0:20:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我的手
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.22,0:20:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,射出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.35,0:20:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,都射这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.76,0:20:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,这样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.36,0:20:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,快点射啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.57,0:20:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.78,0:20:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,没试过这样子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.65,0:20:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,很刺激吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.78,0:20:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.25,0:21:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,很喜欢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.59,0:21:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我什么都知道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.26,0:21:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我说了不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.53,0:21:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,真的要停止吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.07,0:21:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.80,0:21:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,肉棒不是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.94,0:21:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,那叫社员吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.75,0:21:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,不用
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.48,0:21:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,要叫人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.89,0:21:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,要射吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.63,0:21:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,要射了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.70,0:21:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,想要射了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.03,0:21:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,射吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.37,0:21:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.98,0:21:59.97,Default,,0,0,0,,很可怜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.32,0:22:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,没人和你一起
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.06,0:22:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.20,0:22:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.81,0:22:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,很意外啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.21,0:22:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.42,0:22:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.55,0:22:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会告诉别人的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.82,0:22:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,可以说的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.43,0:22:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,要拍照片吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.96,0:22:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,这样子我要生气了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.91,0:23:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,一直在动啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.45,0:23:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.18,0:23:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,没有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.19,0:23:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,很舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.26,0:23:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.88,0:23:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.68,0:23:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.35,0:23:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,这样子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.30,0:23:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,这样子不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.23,0:24:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.12,0:24:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,给我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.52,0:24:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,社长害羞的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.46,0:24:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.14,0:24:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,已经舔了摸了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.34,0:24:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,蛋蛋很硬
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.49,0:24:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,这样不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.69,0:25:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,请吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.04,0:25:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,可以用嘴巴这样
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.71,0:25:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,肉棒硬了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.33,0:25:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.54,0:25:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,不用这样子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.76,0:26:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,一点不舒服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.06,0:26:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,很多女人舔过这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.93,0:26:47.87,Default,,0,0,0,,有很多女人的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.61,0:26:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,这样子舔吗
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.88,0:26:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,社长好大
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.15,0:27:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.29,0:27:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,都是水啊
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.23,0:27:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.20,0:27:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,好香
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.87,0:27:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,很多女人舔过的
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.87,0:28:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,有别的女人的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.81,0:28:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,吃掉了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.81,0:28:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.68,0:28:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,很可怜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.22,0:28:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,要这样子
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.03,0:28:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,女生不会来的
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.10,0:28:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,今天我来安慰你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.97,0:28:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,可以随便做
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.58,0:28:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,让你高潮
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.85,0:28:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.92,0:28:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,要射了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.40,0:29:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,好浓啊
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.67,0:29:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,好多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.81,0:29:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,-在做什么 -很多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.56,0:29:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,这么多
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.71,0:29:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.64,0:29:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,社长很可爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.45,0:29:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,这样子
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.05,0:29:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,要诚实一点
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.88,0:30:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,请吧
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.88,0:30:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.28,0:30:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,现在出去了马上回来
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.69,0:30:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道我去的那个讲座吗
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.29,0:30:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.43,0:30:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,（社长 鲛泽翼）\N不知道吗谁都可以赚钱
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.30,0:30:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,特别受欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.44,0:30:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,也有很多媒体过来
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.05,0:30:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,可能来了一万人
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.79,0:31:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,很厉害吧
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.59,0:31:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,一万啊
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.92,0:31:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,一万人很多的
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.26,0:31:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,-很厉害啊 -这个
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.60,0:31:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,很厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.40,0:31:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,其实卖这个只是赚钱
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.28,0:31:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,其实来的人
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.28,0:31:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,都是喜欢钱的
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.55,0:31:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,只是为了赚钱好玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.96,0:31:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,很舒服的知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.90,0:31:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,今天想和你社长聊聊
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.64,0:31:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,但是不是社长经营
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.11,0:31:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,是的先试试看
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.65,0:32:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,不过呢
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.72,0:32:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,白木今天很厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.46,0:32:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,做他的秘书很可惜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.60,0:32:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.53,0:32:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,要来我这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.81,0:32:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,社长
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.48,0:32:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.08,0:32:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,这么短的裙子
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.03,0:32:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,很厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.03,0:32:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,白木
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.04,0:33:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.17,0:33:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,这是性骚扰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.71,0:33:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.11,0:33:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,做什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.51,0:33:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,社长
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.85,0:33:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我很讨厌被控制
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.39,0:33:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,做什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.13,0:33:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,好疼啊放手
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.26,0:33:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,想要领导社长
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.07,0:33:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我会让他开除你
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.48,0:33:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.68,0:33:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.48,0:33:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,给我
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.08,0:33:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,想要吗
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.95,0:33:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,平常对女孩子用这个了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.43,0:33:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,听话的女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.56,0:33:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,今天
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.83,0:34:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,社长要听话
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.90,0:34:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你到底要做什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.31,0:34:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,可以的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.18,0:34:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,不想这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.78,0:34:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.12,0:34:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,每天都开派对
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.93,0:34:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,适合而止
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.86,0:34:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,有钱
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.80,0:34:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,很多女人都围着你
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.87,0:34:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,说什么都可以
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.01,0:34:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,都是女生很无聊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.88,0:34:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.55,0:34:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,乳头硬了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.15,0:34:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你也是想要钱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.29,0:35:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,想要吗
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.29,0:35:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我有钱放开
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.03,0:35:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我不要的
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.77,0:35:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,只是想控制你
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.51,0:35:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,想控制骄傲的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.91,0:35:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,是我的快感
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.65,0:35:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.59,0:35:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,制服很贵吧
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.32,0:35:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,很贵的 腿放下去
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.46,0:35:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你只是个秘书
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.94,0:35:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,没有被这样子过
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.74,0:35:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,有感觉了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.08,0:35:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,社长舒服了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.88,0:35:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.75,0:36:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,渴了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.56,0:36:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,-渴了吧 -没有
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.29,0:36:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,那给你这个
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.10,0:36:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.77,0:36:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,舌头伸出来等着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.57,0:36:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,-还想要吧 -不想
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.31,0:36:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,好脏啊不要
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.73,0:36:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,谁让你这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.73,0:36:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,有反应了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.74,0:36:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.41,0:36:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,大家看到了会吓到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.88,0:37:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.62,0:37:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,谁让你摸的
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.83,0:37:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,做什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.63,0:37:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,这样子
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.37,0:37:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,不要摸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.31,0:37:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,不要摸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.71,0:37:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,这之后
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.18,0:37:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.11,0:37:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,之后
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.98,0:37:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,要开会
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.52,0:37:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.00,0:37:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,好吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.87,0:37:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.14,0:37:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,很听话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.74,0:38:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,社长想要什么
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.81,0:38:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,秘书都知道
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.95,0:38:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,不要啊 西装要弄脏了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.29,0:38:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,那给你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.23,0:38:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,那嘴巴
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.76,0:38:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,想弄嘴里
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.43,0:38:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,不要啊
